            We must with all our Majesty and skill |
            Both countenance and excuse. Ho Guydelstern," amendedText="
            But we will ship him hence, |
            Ho Guydelstern, and Rosencraus,"/>
        
        <substitution method="pen" type="replacement" copyText="
            Into the Chappel; I pray you haste in this: |
            Come Gertrard we'll call up our wisest friends," amendedText="
            Into the Chappel; |
            Come madam [deleted] we'll call up our wisest friends,"/>
        
